{"tid":565812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡擬調升消費稅至9%","createTime":"2018-02-19T10:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T10:57:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e6fb5a1add3fcefe0d0f8a6c39c46461b39c82a","tid":565812,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180219/large/1519035655_f3b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180219%2Flarge%2F1519035655_f3b1.jpg&h=94a531e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新加坡政府公布2018/19年度財政預算案，為應付未來社會於基建及教育等方面的增加開支，預算案提出於2021年至2025年間上調消費稅 (GST）兩個百分點，由目前7%增至9%，具體推出時間則視乎當地經濟及開支情況而定。<br />\n<br />\n此外，新加坡亦計畫課徵每噸5元新幣碳稅（carbon tax）。自2020年起亦會向進口服務課徵e-tax，包括網上影片及音樂串流平台等。"},{"pid":"7f6460c3224790620b6926011cef8fd4050f20f6","tid":565812,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:56:33.000Z","msg":"李家坡萬稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbfb725ebfa98c9b835469331e6c45c2c8f202a","tid":565812,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"唔去就無影響"}]}